## How to run the MCP
- after creating your venv
- activate source "/Your path to file location/futher-mcp/venv/bin/activate"    
- install requirements "pip install requirements.txt"
- Start the server " PYTHONPATH=src uvicorn further_mcp.fastapi_server:APP --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000" {in Linux}

